          <div class="column has-text-centered" style="color:white;">
            <h4 style="font-weight:bold;color:yellow;font-size: 1.5em;text-shadow: 1px 1px 1px darkblue, 1px 1px 3px darkblue;">Eat Chocopie Together for Global Peace</h4>
            <br/>
            Click the map to share a virtual Chocopie with a friend. Your participation raises funds for the <a href="/about#giving-back">Korean
            American Community Foundation COVID-19 Action Fund</a> to support those affected by the Coronavirus, and to stand against anti-Asian racism. <a href="/howitworks">Learn more</a>
          <br/><br/>
            Part of the <a href="http://asiasocietytriennial.org" target="_blank">Asia Society Triennial: <em>We Do Not Dream Alone</em></a>
          </div>
          
          <div class="column is-half">
            <div id="main-map">
              <svg height="100%" width="100%" viewBox="0 0 75 100">
                <g></g>
              </svg>
              <span class="icon main-map__loading">
                <i class="fas fa-spinner fa-pulse"></i>
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
          
