            </div>
          <div class="column">
            <p>
              Your Chocopie has been shared and $1 has been automatically raised in your name towards the <a href="/about#giving-back">Korean American Community Foundation COVID-19 Action Fund</a>. 
          Feel free to <a href="/">share another Chocopie</a> or share this image on your social media to spread this positive initiative. 
            <br/><br/>
  Don’t miss Mina Cheon’s artwork installed in the Asia Society Museum in Part 2: March 16, 2021 – June 27, 2021 as well as her special installation of the physical “Eat Chocopie Together.” 
            <br/><br/>
          <small>Don't see the Chocopie email? Please check in your spam folder, you might just find it there.</small>
        </p>
